title: Fingerprint Technician - Fingerprint Capture Training
description: This is a sample video for testing
summary: The image sequence appears to show a series of screenshots from an online training course focused on fingerprint scanning. The course, titled "Fingerprint Technician - Fingerprint Capture Training," is designed to train technicians on the proper techniques and procedures for capturing fingerprints. The screenshots depict various stages of the course, including the initial launch, progress tracking, and completion notifications. The training module is part of Delta Air Lines' efforts to ensure their fingerprint technicians are well-equipped to maintain compliance with government regulations. The interface includes options for launching the content, tracking progress, and exiting the course, providing a comprehensive learning experience for the technicians.
